The KDE series contains the KDE Plasma Desktop for Wayland and X.

Installation sudo apt install task-kde-desktop konsole plasma-welcome konqueror sddm-theme-breeze  -y
After install run sudo apt remove desktop-base -y then sudo apt purge desktop-base -y
Then run sudo systemctl enable sddm then sudo systemctl start sddm
Login to KDE Plasma
Then on Login Screen SDDM select Breeze theme instead of Ubuntu Budgie
Then sudo apt autoremove -y

For i686

Make sure you have enough storage and memory

Installation sudo apt install plasma-desktop sddm konsole xinit plasma-discover -y
